<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - ABC High School</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Inline styles for developer section to avoid modifying styles.css */
        .developer-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1C2526 0%, #34495E 100%);
            padding: 80px 20px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .developer-card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .developer-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
        .developer-photo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            border: 3px solid #2980B9;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .developer-photo:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(41, 128, 185, 0.7);
        }
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .social-button {
            background-color: #2980B9;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .social-button:hover {
            background-color: #3498DB;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/header', { activePage: 'about' }) %>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero" data-animate="fade-in">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h2>About ABC High School</h2>
                <p>Discover Our Mission, Vision, and the Passionate Developer Behind This Platform</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About School Section -->
        <section class="about" data-animate="slide-up">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Founded with a commitment to excellence, ABC High School is dedicated to nurturing young minds and preparing students for a bright future. Our innovative curriculum, state-of-the-art facilities, and passionate educators create an environment where creativity, critical thinking, and personal growth thrive.</p>
                <p>We believe in empowering students to become leaders, thinkers, and changemakers. Our student management system, built with cutting-edge technology, ensures seamless access to records, fostering transparency and efficiency for students, parents, and faculty.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Meet the Developer Section -->
        <section class="developer-section" data-animate="slide-up">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Meet the Developer</h2>
                <div class="developer-card" data-animate="fade-in">
                    <img src="https://annu-portfolio.onrender.com/images/IMG_2694.png" alt="Annu Mudgal" class="developer-photo">
                    <h3>Annu Mudgal</h3>
                    <p>Hi, I'm Annu Mudgal, a passionate software developer with a knack for building sleek, user-friendly web applications. I crafted this student management system for ABC High School using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and EJS, ensuring a seamless experience for managing student records. My goal is to create technology that empowers and inspires. Explore my work and connect with me!</p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="https://github.com/annumudgal001" class="social-button" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/annumudgal001/" class="social-button" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
                        <a href="https://annu-portfolio.onrender.com" class="social-button" target="_blank">Portfolio</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>